Your first post, welcome to the forums. 

You can probably just ignore those errors if KSP is working ok. It's a common error with some mods. I get similar error messages and my game runs well.

Here's more info about the error (in the context of one specific mod) with a suggested workaround by an esteemed modder. I have never tried this workaround. https://github.com/jrbudda/KerbalEngineer/issues/52
Im gonna be honest I got no Idea what these errors are but I would try verifying your install reinstalling your mods especially EVE and making sure you have all dependencies
